movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: Bravo To All Involved
review: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace is nothing short of spectacular. Great congratulations go out to all involved in creating this epic, most notably Industrial Light and Magic, for amazing effects, John Williams, for an excellent score, and, of course, George Lucas, for obvious reasons.  I encourage anyone, Star Wars fan or not, to see this movie.
